  "body": "I run two geth nodes, one on Rinkeby and one on the mainnet. Previously syncing had been going very well, but I came onsite today to discover that both nodes are behind in sync, and are also completely unable to find any peers. There's no debug information of any kind that is making it clear what exactly is going wrong. I have permitted firewall rules for 30303 TCP/UDP, NTP, and DNS, but still none of my nodes can find any peers.",
